					"patching_rect" : [ 134.5, 115.0, 234.0, 222.0 ],
					"text" : "The 'menu' parameter (or 'menu_' prefix) generates a Dropdown Widget in VCV Rack. \n\nBecause we set @min 1 and @max 4, the build script will automatically detect that this menu requires exactly 4 items. During the build, it will interactively ask you to name them (e.g., 1=Sine, 2=Triangle, 3=Saw, 4=Square).\n\nThe parameter outputs an integer (1 to 4) directly into the selector~, dynamically swapping the wavefolder's source audio\n"
